34WebKitDecoderReceiver::WebKitDecoderReceiver(VTVideoDecoderSession session)
35 : m_session(session)
36{
37}
38
39WebKitDecoderReceiver::~WebKitDecoderReceiver()
40{
41 if (m_pixelBufferPool)
42 CFRelease(m_pixelBufferPool);
43}
44
45void WebKitDecoderReceiver::initializeFromFormatDescription(CMFormatDescriptionRef formatDescription)
46{
47 // CoreAnimation doesn't support full-planar YUV, so we must convert the buffers output
48 // by libvpx to bi-planar YUV. Create pixel buffer attributes and give those to the
49 // decoder session for use in creating its own internal CVPixelBufferPool, which we
50 // will use post-decode.
51 m_isFullRange = false;
52 m_is10bit = false;
53
54 auto extensions = CMFormatDescriptionGetExtensions(formatDescription);
55 if (!extensions)
56 return;
57
58 CFTypeRef extensionAtoms = CFDictionaryGetValue(extensions, kCMFormatDescriptionExtension_SampleDescriptionExtensionAtoms);
59 if (!extensionAtoms || CFGetTypeID(extensionAtoms) != CFDictionaryGetTypeID())
60 return;
61
62 auto configurationRecord = static_cast<CFDataRef>(CFDictionaryGetValue((CFDictionaryRef)extensionAtoms, CFSTR("vpcC")));
63 if (!configurationRecord || CFGetTypeID(configurationRecord) != CFDataGetTypeID())
64 return;
65
66 auto configurationRecordSize = CFDataGetLength(configurationRecord);
67 if (configurationRecordSize < 12)
68 return;
69
70 auto configurationRecordData = CFDataGetBytePtr(configurationRecord);
71 auto bitDepthChromaAndRange = *(configurationRecordData + 6);
72
73 if ((bitDepthChromaAndRange >> 4) == 10)
74 m_is10bit = true;
75
76 if (bitDepthChromaAndRange & 0x1)
77 m_isFullRange = true;
78}
79
80CVPixelBufferPoolRef WebKitDecoderReceiver::pixelBufferPool(size_t pixelBufferWidth, size_t pixelBufferHeight, bool is10bit)
81{
82 if (m_pixelBufferPool && m_pixelBufferWidth == pixelBufferWidth && m_pixelBufferHeight == pixelBufferHeight && m_is10bit == is10bit)
83 return m_pixelBufferPool;
84
85 OSType pixelFormat;
86 if (is10bit)
87 pixelFormat = m_isFullRange ? kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr10BiPlanarFullRange : kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr10BiPlanarVideoRange;
88 else
89 pixelFormat = m_isFullRange ? kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr8BiPlanarFullRange : kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr8BiPlanarVideoRange;
90
91 auto createPixelFormatAttributes = [] (OSType pixelFormat) {
92 auto createNumber = [] (int32_t format) -> CFNumberRef {
93 return CFNumberCreate(kCFAllocatorDefault, kCFNumberSInt32Type, &format);
94 };
95 auto cfPixelFormats = CFArrayCreateMutable(kCFAllocatorDefault, 2, &kCFTypeArrayCallBacks);
96 auto formatNumber = createNumber(pixelFormat);
97 CFArrayAppendValue(cfPixelFormats, formatNumber);
98 CFRelease(formatNumber);
99
100 auto borderPixelsValue = createNumber(32);
101
102 const void* keys[] = {
103 kCVPixelBufferPixelFormatTypeKey,
104 kCVPixelBufferExtendedPixelsLeftKey,
105 kCVPixelBufferExtendedPixelsRightKey,
106 kCVPixelBufferExtendedPixelsTopKey,
107 kCVPixelBufferExtendedPixelsBottomKey,
108 };
109 const void* values[] = {
110 cfPixelFormats,
111 borderPixelsValue,
112 borderPixelsValue,
113 borderPixelsValue,
114 borderPixelsValue,
115 };
116 auto attributes = CFDictionaryCreate(kCFAllocatorDefault, keys, values, std::size(keys), &kCFTypeDictionaryKeyCallBacks, &kCFTypeDictionaryValueCallBacks);
117 CFRelease(borderPixelsValue);
118 CFRelease(cfPixelFormats);
119 return attributes;
120 };
121
122 auto pixelBufferAttributes = createPixelFormatAttributes(pixelFormat);
123 VTDecoderSessionSetPixelBufferAttributes(m_session, pixelBufferAttributes);
124 CFRelease(pixelBufferAttributes);
125
126 if (m_pixelBufferPool) {
127 CFRelease(m_pixelBufferPool);
128 m_pixelBufferPool = nullptr;
129 }
130
131 m_pixelBufferPool = VTDecoderSessionGetPixelBufferPool(m_session);
132 if (m_pixelBufferPool)
133 CFRetain(m_pixelBufferPool);
134
135 m_pixelBufferWidth = pixelBufferWidth;
136 m_pixelBufferHeight = pixelBufferHeight;
137 m_is10bit = is10bit;
138
139 return m_pixelBufferPool;
140}
141
142OSStatus WebKitDecoderReceiver::decoderFailed(int error)
143{
144 OSStatus vtError;
145 if (error == WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_NO_OUTPUT)
146 vtError = noErr;
147 else if (error == WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_UNINITIALIZED)
148 vtError = kVTVideoDecoderMalfunctionErr;
149 else if (error == WEBRTC_VIDEO_CODEC_MEMORY)
150 vtError = kVTAllocationFailedErr;
151 else
152 vtError = kVTVideoDecoderBadDataErr;
153
154 VTDecoderSessionEmitDecodedFrame(m_session, m_currentFrame, vtError, 0, nullptr);
155 m_currentFrame = nullptr;
156
157 RTC_LOG(LS_ERROR) << "VP9 decoder: decoder failed with error " << error << ", vtError " << vtError;
158 return vtError;
159}
160
161int32_t WebKitDecoderReceiver::Decoded(VideoFrame& frame)
162{
163 auto pixelBuffer = pixelBufferFromFrame(frame, [this](size_t width, size_t height, BufferType type) -> CVPixelBufferRef {
164 auto pixelBufferPool = this->pixelBufferPool(width, height, type == BufferType::I010);
165 if (!pixelBufferPool)
166 return nullptr;
167
168 CVPixelBufferRef pixelBuffer = nullptr;
169 if (CVPixelBufferPoolCreatePixelBuffer(kCFAllocatorDefault, m_pixelBufferPool, &pixelBuffer) == kCVReturnSuccess)
170 return pixelBuffer;
171 return nullptr;
172 });
173
174 VTDecoderSessionEmitDecodedFrame(m_session, m_currentFrame, pixelBuffer ? noErr : -1, 0, pixelBuffer);
175 m_currentFrame = nullptr;
176 if (pixelBuffer)
177 CFRelease(pixelBuffer);
178 return 0;
179}
180
181int32_t WebKitDecoderReceiver::Decoded(VideoFrame& frame, int64_t)
182{
183 Decoded(frame);
184 return 0;
185}
186
187void WebKitDecoderReceiver::Decoded(VideoFrame& frame, absl::optional<int32_t>, absl::optional<uint8_t>)
188{
189 Decoded(frame);
190}
